OL,3,CTeenage motorcyclist critically
OL,4,Cinjured in Dorset crash
OL,6,FA teenage motorcyclist is critically
OL,7,Finjured in hospital after his
OL,8,Fmotorbike crashed on Hurn Road near
OL,9,FRingwood.
OL,11,FDorset Police were called to the scene
OL,12,Fat 4.18pm on Saturday 11 April
OL,13,Ffollowing reports of a single-vehicle
OL,14,Fcollision between Avon Avenue and Avon
OL,15,FCastle Road.
OL,17,FThe vehicle involved was a white KTM
OL,18,Fmotorcycle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
