OL,3,CTeenage motorcyclist critically
OL,4,Cinjured in Dorset crash
OL,6,FEmergency services attended and the
OL,7,Fmotorcyclist ` an 18-year-old man `
OL,8,Fwas taken to hospital with injuries
OL,9,Fthat are believed to be potentially
OL,10,Flife-threatening. His family has been
OL,11,Finformed.
OL,13,FRoad closures were put in place to
OL,14,Fallow the emergency services to
OL,15,Frespond and for an examination of the
OL,16,Fscene to be carried out.
