OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776066987
OL,3,CTeenage motorcyclist critically
OL,4,Cinjured in Dorset crash
OL,6,FSergeant Dave Cotterill, of the Roads
OL,7,FPolicing Team, said: "We are carrying
OL,8,Fout enquiries to establish the full
OL,9,Fcircumstances of this collision and I
OL,10,Fam keen to hear from any witnesses who
OL,11,Fhave not already spoken to police.
OL,13,F"I would also urge anyone who was
OL,14,Ftravelling in the area of Hurn Road
OL,15,Faround the relevant time to please
OL,16,Fcheck any dashcam footage to see if
OL,17,Fthey have captured anything that might
OL,18,Fassist our investigation.
