PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776066987
OL,3,CTeenage motorcyclist critically
OL,4,Cinjured in Dorset crash
OL,6,F"Finally, I would like to thank
OL,7,Fmotorists for their patience and
OL,8,Funderstanding during the road
OL,9,Fclosures. These are necessary to allow
OL,10,Fthe emergency services to safely
OL,11,Frespond and for a thorough examination
OL,12,Fof the scene to be conducted."
OL,14,FA fatal collision occurred on the same
OL,15,Fstretch of road in September 2023
OL,17,FLaionie Kennard, 18, sadly died and
OL,18,Fthree other teenagers were injured
OL,19,Fafter their car came of the road.
